    "path": "src/client",
    "name": "client",
    "purpose": "Client crate namespace for the marix_client library and client binaries. ClientEvent carries Common streaming output and Done completion events by signature id, and ClientSession connects to the server over the client channel selected by ChannelEndpoint::Client, creates tasks with an empty TaskSignature.name, and keeps the user request only in TaskEvent::Create.",
